1. Find graphics, an abandonware game should be good enough. No licensing problems.
2. Find a way to use graphics from this game for our own.
3. Design graphics and levels.
4. Design enemies and bosses.
5. Design UI.
6. Program it all.
7. Get a working prototype, one enemy and one level.
8. Implement eye-candy and finish all else, including the UI.
9. Celebrate!
